---

<section class="min-h-screen flex items-center pt-24 pb-32 px-8 bg-surface">
  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[1280px] grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 pr-8">
      <h1 class="text-[48px] font-bold leading-[1.2] tracking-[-0.02em] text-on-surface">
        São 6 da manhã...<br />Quem você visita primeiro?
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl leading-[1.6] text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl">
        A decisão de vender exige foco. A gestão da sua rotina não deveria competir por ele. Otimize suas visitas com precisão.
      </p>
      <div>
        <a href="https://app.medivisitas.com/signup" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded bg-primary px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-on-primary transition-colors hover:bg-surface-tint">
          Assumir o Controle
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant rounded-xl p-8 h-[500px] flex flex-col items-center justify-center shadow-sm">
      <div class="absolute top-8 left-8 text-outline">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[48px]">schedule</span>
      </div>
      <div class="text-[72px] font-bold leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.04em] text-primary mb-8">
        06:00<span class="text-[36px] font-semibold text-outline ml-2">AM</span>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full max-w-md flex flex-col gap-4 border-t border-outline-variant pt-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 bg-surface rounded border border-outline-variant">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-error"></div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-base font-semibold text-on-surface">Dr. Silva — Moinhos</div>
              <div class="text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-on-surface-variant mt-1">URGENTE</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-outline">priority_high</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 bg-surface rounded border border-outline-variant opacity-50">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-secondary"></div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-base font-semibold text-on-surface">Dr. Costa — PUC</div>
              <div class="text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-on-surface-variant mt-1">ALTA PREVISTA</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-outline">check_circle</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
